713753f-a.title: Manhattan: 55th Street - Sutton Place South
713753f-a.text:
55th Street, north side, west from and including Sutton Place South (formerly Avenue A). At Ehe N. W. corner of First Avenue may be seen the spire of the Roman Catholic Church of St.John
the Evangelist.
December 6, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
